properties.description: 2016 Extended Ortophotos, Moldova, Scale 1:5000, 20cm, true colours, covers practically the entire territory of the Republic of Moldova, except some areas from the east part of Moldova,compared to original 2016 Ortophotos, these are extended with about 2-5 km at the boundaries.
